Interface Summary

Log Simple logger TODO - use some logging framework !
MainMenu Paints Main Menu and adds listeners to it.
Picture This class handles all of the painting.
Point Basic point class.
SpriteBase Base abstract class for all sprites.
Triangle Triangle class made up of 3 Points.
Vertex Same as Point class, but has 3 coordinates: X, Y, and Z.
